Module dual.engine.apply.call.

Rule twice given n, produce:
  Return n times 2.

Rule countdown given stars, produce:
  Return apply countdown to stars minus 1.

Rule run given seed, produce:
  Return apply twice to seed plus 1.

Rule wrap given x, produce:
  Return apply Some to x.

Rule rightOperand given a, b, produce:
  Return a plus apply twice to b plus 1.

Rule return given x, produce:
  Return x times 3.

Rule viaSoftKeyword given x, produce:
  Return apply return to x.
